# Environment — Simple Roster Plus (repo root)

Copy to `.env` in this directory and adjust.

```bash
# PostgreSQL connection string used by Prisma
DATABASE_URL="postgresql://USER:PASSWORD@localhost:5432/simple_roster_plus?schema=public"

# Used for session signing when auth is added (min 16 chars in production)
AUTH_SECRET="change-me-in-development-only"
```

Do not commit real secrets. `.env` is gitignored by Next.js defaults.
